4
00:00:18,185 --> 00:00:29,649
[SPEAKER_00]: Curtis Tufts accommodates students with a variety of learning differences who are on an individualized education plan and have struggled in a traditional classroom setting.

5
00:00:30,569 --> 00:00:33,151
[SPEAKER_00]: You will find that student success is our priority.

6
00:00:33,991 --> 00:00:40,356
[SPEAKER_00]: The Curtis-Tufts focuses on meeting the individual needs of all students through differentiated learning.

7
00:00:41,337 --> 00:00:49,642
[SPEAKER_00]: Students learn in an intimate setting with class size that is limited to eight students and a maximum school total of 40 students.

8
00:00:50,403 --> 00:00:58,248
[SPEAKER_00]: The Curtis-Tufts is fully staffed with highly qualified professionals, including teachers, adjustment Councilors, and a building administrator.

9
00:00:59,389 --> 00:01:08,494
[SPEAKER_00]: Each year will provide important transitions and the acquisition of new skills that will enhance students' ability to apply learning in many ways.

10
00:01:09,615 --> 00:01:20,841
[SPEAKER_00]: We are committed to providing a challenging and rigorous curriculum that helps each student progress at a developmentally appropriate rate and provides a safe environment for all students.

11
00:01:22,242 --> 00:01:23,503
[SPEAKER_00]: Mother Teresa has said,

12
00:01:24,252 --> 00:01:26,213
[SPEAKER_00]: In this life, we cannot do great things.

13
00:01:26,533 --> 00:01:29,134
[SPEAKER_00]: We can only do small things with great love.

14
00:01:30,034 --> 00:01:40,378
