15
00:01:41,018 --> 00:01:51,862
[SPEAKER_00]: Teaching and learning offers us all numerous opportunities to focus on a number of small things that culminate over time to produce students that are prepared to do the great things of life.

16
00:01:53,082 --> 00:02:03,526
[SPEAKER_00]: With this in mind, ultimately, as a school community, we are judged by the actions of our students and the way new student learning connects and impacts the world beyond our school.

17
