19
00:02:20,856 --> 00:02:29,424
[SPEAKER_00]: I aim to make our students' learning experience at Curtis Tufts engaging and exciting by working in partnership with our students' families and guardians.

20
00:02:30,305 --> 00:02:40,330
[SPEAKER_00]: As the new principal of Curtis Tufts, I believe that it is my responsibility to maintain and to continue to build a supportive and collaborative spirit at our school.

21
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:52,936
